content.text: Answer only what is written in the image, single word

Based on this application description, generate a short, concise name suitable for use as a GitHub repository name.
The name should be lowercase with words separated by hyphens (kebab-case) and should not include any special characters.
Application description: "A simple web application with a single button. When the button is clicked, a counter increments. The counter's value is persisted in a database and displayed on the frontend. There is no user authentication. The UI should be clean and minimalist."
Return ONLY the name, nothing else.
